title: Weider X-Factor ST + Guides and Logs
description:
Designed to transform your body, this 8-week progressive program trains you in the Optimization Zone from the core out to maximize time and increase results. Each week is progressively harder so you grow with the program to get the body you want. The Weider X-Factor: ST includes eight 30-minute workout DVDs, four bonus workout DVDs, an 8-week Nutrition Guide, fitness journal, workout calendar and rotating push-up stands for incredible, core-sculpting results!
